So the other day Julius went up to my locker holding his phone and he reminded me that it was roughly around this time last year that julius, troy, and i one day went to julius' basement to "practice". We ended up playing some My American Heart songs. Boy those were some great times. 
Reminiscing...i decided to find out what's been happening to the band.
